column2: Oh god oh fuck there's so many jellies!
Hell yeah, look at those jellies to kill!
Uh, uh, uh, the enemy forces are significantly larger both in number and in physical morphology than the current Republic data suggested!
Here I stand. Here I begin my true quest to avenge my father.
Can't even scavenge those corpses. Useless.
Keheheh, can't wait to see which of you gets melted first.
Wow, that's a lot of jellies!
Right, chaps! Direct frontal assault along with Green and Blue teams! Forward!
